# UI Package Guidelines

- Follow project-wide standards in `.cursor/rules/project-guidelines.mdc`.
- Shared React component library using `shadcn/ui`.
- Components must live in `src/components/` (e.g., Button, Card, Avatar, Typography, ThemeProvider).
- Styles go in `src/styles/globals.css`.
- Utilities in `src/lib/` (e.g., utils.ts).
- Follow `shadcn/ui` naming conventions.
- Use `@repo/ui` for any reusable UI elements across apps.
- To add components, use `npx shadcn@latest add <component>` from an app directory.
- For build and deploy, see Turborepo docs: https://turbo.build/repo/docs

